{"TopicId":3167,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How do I make a poll?","CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-10-23T16:33:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-10-23T16:33:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow do I make a poll before a thread? I\\\u0027ve seen people do it but I have no idea how to. Anyone help please?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt\u0026#039;n Skunky","CreatedById":1261,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-10-23T17:18:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mincespy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022mincespy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow do I make a poll before a thread? I\\\u0027ve seen people do it but I have no idea how to. Anyone help please?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERight next to the New Topic button you used to make this post is a New Poll button. Try that.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EArrr!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECapt\\\u0027n Skunky\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mincespy","CreatedById":9003,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-10-23T17:47:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOkay, thanks! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SchildConstruct","CreatedById":10241,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-10-23T17:53:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mincespy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022mincespy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOkay, thanks! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt doesn\\\u0027t work in \u003Cem\u003Eall\u003C/em\u003E sub-fora. But in Off Topic it \u003Cem\u003Edoes\u003C/em\u003E work.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt\u0026#039;n Skunky","CreatedById":1261,"CreatedDateTime":"2011-10-23T18:28:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SchildConstruct\u0022 data-cite=\u0022SchildConstruct\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt doesn\\\u0027t work in \u003Cem\u003Eall\u003C/em\u003E sub-fora. But in Off Topic it \u003Cem\u003Edoes\u003C/em\u003E work.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is true, the forum must be set to allow it. This can be set on a per forum basis so the feature may not be available in them all.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EArrr!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECapt\\\u0027n Skunky\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}